(numRobEntries, area_cell_area).explanation: Increasing the number of ROB entries requires more physical storage cells in the processor, directly increasing the total cell area needed for implementation;

(numRobEntries, power_register).explanation: More ROB entries mean more register storage elements that consume power for maintaining state, directly increasing register power consumption;

(numRobEntries, nL2TLBEntries).explanation: The number of ROB entries and L2 TLB entries are independent design parameters that serve different functions in the processor pipeline;
